\cf3\lang1033\f1\fs32 &\f0  \cf4\ul HISTORY\cf1\lang1048\b\fs24\par
\cf2\ulnone\b0 This program is based on a very old video game that was first seen  in arcade halls and portable game systems, then on more advanced machines, like the ZX Spectrum, etc. Unfortunately, in today's world of 1st-person 3D games, strategic simulations and flight simulators, everybody tends to forget these old, but fun games and play all of that 3D stuff, which seems fun at the beginning, but which hides behind the realism and the dazzling special FX the same old ideas. This PC version, written by D.C.M. SOFT, ressurects this good ol'game with new graphics and sound to show you that even old arcade games can be fun nowadays. I'm not asking you to delete all the new 3D games from your hard drive (and thus increase the free space by 1500 MB \lang1024\f1 J\lang1048\f0  ). Just take a break from your F-29 flight simulator and enjoy this nice colurful game when you need to play something simple, that doesn't require 23 commands just to get from one place to another \lang1024\f1 J\lang1048\f0 . And if \b you\b0  don't like it, see if your kids do...\par
